dct_title_s: Gard, Anduze : echelle du 1/2000e, plan topographique régulier
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, hachures, and spot heights. "Complété á l'aide des photographies aériennes." "Coordonnées Lambert III." Oriented with north towards upper right corner. "Reproduction interdite." Shows some street names, railways, parks.
dct_creator_sm: France. Ministère de la reconstruction et du logement
dct_publisher_sm: France : Ministère de la reconstruction et de l'urbanisme, 1955.
